::Perndabot::

Cloaked, Perndabot makes his way toward the CF. He hoped that they wouldn't 
launch an external scanner sweep any time soon. The huge Alliance bot stops 
behind Cybershark, making no noise. He would enter after this bot, and then 
find the brig.
